{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_15_01",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 1話 私が署長なんですから",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、すみれ。こんな所にいたのか\nわざわざ屋上に来て、何か気になることがあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 8.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "高層ビルの屋上からだと、遠くまでよく見えるなぁ\n……ん？　あそこの人、何してるんだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "うわ！？\nそんなに柵から身を乗り出したら危ないぞ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 533.3329519000004,
          "startTime": 19.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 22.8000003815
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ、{user}さん？\nそんなに慌ててどうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なんでって、すみれが屋上から落ちそうになってたら\nそりゃ、焦りもするだろう！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 33.1000007629
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　私が屋上から落ちる？\n……あ、地上にいる人を見てたからかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 40.9000011444
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "あそこを歩いてた人が、なんだか妙な動きをしてたので\n気になって、思わず下を覗き込んじゃったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "でも大丈夫ですよ。ほら、柵はしっかり握ってますし\n絶対に手を離したりはしませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 57.0666678111
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ならいいけど、事故には本当に気を付けてくれよ\nそれにしても、なんで一人で屋上なんかに来たんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 65.5666681926
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "それは……今度やるミュージカルの役のことで\nちょっと、悩んでるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 72.7666784923
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "『空の宝石』のことか？\n確か、宝石の体と永遠の命を持つ妖精の話だったよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 80.6999964396
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "はい。私がエメラルド、優ちゃんがアメジストの妖精で\n瑠依ちゃんは人間族の女の子の役ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "妖精と人間族は、価値観や考え方が違うけど\n私達は仲良くなって、一緒に危機に立ち向かう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 98.6333415985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺は、すみれにぴったりの役だと思ってたんだけどなぁ\nどういうところの演技で悩んでるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "妖精の役をやるのは初めてなので\nどう演じたらいいのかも、まだまだ手探りですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 112.1333415985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "それと、人間族の瑠依ちゃんを助ける場面で\n妖精の私は、高い所から舞い降りるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "前にフライボードをやったこともありますし\nバルコニーから降りるくらい簡単だと思ったんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 128.2333415985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "その……いざ、舞台に飛び降りようとしたら\n何度やっても、足がすくんじゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今回はバンジージャンプみたいなものだからなぁ\n自分から飛び込むのが怖いのは、当然だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 143.8333344777
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……妖精を演じるからには\n飛ぶシーンはあるに越したことはないんだろうけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、すみれの安全が第一だ\n俺から演出家の方に掛け合ってみようか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 156.999979655
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、演出家さんも「無理してやらなくてもいい」と\n言ってくれてるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "でも空も飛べない妖精なんて、見てて面白くないし\n瑠依ちゃんを助けられないのは、悔しいですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.4333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 172.9000030518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "それで、高い所に慣れれば\n怖い気持ちも薄れるかなって思ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 178.8666525524
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどな\nとは言え、すぐに耐性がつくものでもないよなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tvrooftop-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "tvtop",
      "startTime": 184.633298874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire Okuyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_15_01-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "はい……何か一つ、きっかけがあれば\n吹っ切れたり、平気になったりするんでしょうか？",
